<item>
            <title>[SOLR-825] The ConstantScore family of queries does not work with highlighting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-825</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Would be nice to be able to highlight range, wildcard, prefix queries again. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1424&quot; title=&quot;Change all multi-term querys so that they extend MultiTermQuery and allow for a constant score mode&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUCENE-1424&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-1424&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1425&quot; title=&quot;Add ConstantScore highlighting support to SpanScorer&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUCENE-1425&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-1425&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, updating Lucene jars, and a patch from this issue, will get us there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
